- create a feature that makes it annoy to use the device by 
  - making the screen grayscale
  - disabling sound or making it very low
  - making internet very slow 
  - bluring videos 
  - creating random funny objects and letting move across the screen on top of everything else

- Let the user create regulations using DevicePolicyManager if the underlying os is android

- Let the user create regulations for other devices running android using Android Management API.